jQuery Flower Navigation Plugin

Version b0.1

Date Created: 28-03-2011 by Philipp Urlich


Description:

This plugin transforms an ul list into a craousel flower type navigation. There's several uses for this plugin. With CSS and additional JS functions and events you can use this as a traditional navigation or as a picture galerie.

How to use:

<script>

	//basic initialisation
	$('#nav').flowernav();

	// different settings
	$('#nav').flowernav({'radius': 200});

</script>